|CKBDarkwind Lottery
|WKO-----------------------------------------------------------------------

|YKOThe Darkwind lottery system allows players to gamble to try to better
themselves, and their pocket books.

The lottery is played once per boot, with a winner chosen 2 days into
a boot. A reminder is given 30 minutes, 10 minutes, and 1 minute before
the end of the lottery.

The lottery system works much like a raffle - players buy tickets for
the lottery, bettering their overall odds of winning. Players may only
buy 75 tickets, per lottery, at 1000 coins per ticket.

The prize pot is directly dependent on the total number of tickets
sold to the lottery, therefore it's important to get as many of your
friends to buy tickets as possible.

It is not guaranteed that a winner will be chosen for each lottery. If
no winner is chosen, the prize pot will be saved and added to the next
boot lottery.

